       If you already did this very hard problem,  you have done
half a work, and you can also begin to be happy to have got half 
a tower. But it isn't finished it. Now you have to assemble EVE-
RYTHING. Prepare to work a lot (I worked about 1 week and then I
was bored because I was tired to look for  some piece I couldn't 
find out, like the video port connector), and to try and try un-
til everything will be ok. 
        


